  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining Project Showcase**\n\nOkay, I\'m working on the architecture for an interactive project showcase component, specifically `/src/components/ProjectShowcase.tsx`. I\'m planning to include projects categorized as \"Fullstack\", \"Frontend\", \"Architecture\", and \"AI.\" I think this component will be interactive and allow for filtering.\n\n\n**Designing Project Showcase Content**\n\nI\'ve decided on four showcase projects: OmniSearch Cloud Hub (Fullstack), Recognito Canvas Core (AI/WebGL), Hydra Stream Engine (Architecture), and Stellar UI Component Kit (Frontend). Each will represent elite craft. I\'m imagining filter tabs, hover states with scaling and glow, and interactive modals with detailed descriptions, features, impact indicators, tech stack, and links. I will build this component with `create_file` at `/src/components/ProjectShowcase.tsx`.\n\n\n"
