  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Summarizing the Design**\n\nI\'ve just finalized the clean-up and am ready to present the design summary. I\'ve structured it according to the specified communication style. My voice will be friendly, professional, and helpful. I\'ll maintain objectivity, avoiding self-promotion and focusing entirely on functional and visual highlights for easy human scanning.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed building your interactive premium developer portfolio inspired by the high-contrast, futuristic design theme of **Recognito**. \n\nThe application is fully responsive, highly performant, and ready for showcase. Here is a high-level overview of the visual theme, layout components, and animations crafted into the application:\n\n### \360\237\214\214 Visual Identity & Theme\n*   **Volcanic Amber Aesthetic**: Grounded on a deep obsidian canvas (`#080808` / `bg-neutral-950`) contrasted with glowing orange and amber ambient lighting nodes that simulate real-time depth.\n*   **Unified Typography**: Pairings of **Plus Jakarta Sans** for body interfaces, **Space Grotesk** for display-oriented headers, and **JetBrains Mono** for technical codeblocks and interactive terminal logs.\n*   **Flawless Dark Mode Toggle**: Supports fluid transition swaps between the deep neon amber workspace and a high-contrast sand-off-white light mode.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\247\261 Grid Layout & Components\n*   **Vertical Slats Grid Overlay**: The entire viewport layout is split into 10 column panels (`grid-cols-10`) separated by subtle micro-thin right borders. Behind the columns, individual glowing circular assets shift to create a sliced glitched wave or vertical equalizer visual.\n*   **Orbital Core Centerpiece**: A heavy concentric sphere anchored in the hero workspace featuring rotating 3D orbit rings, hovering spring-based dampening, and custom monogram markings.\n*   **Floating HUD Nodes**: Small glassmorphic nodes scattered over the grid layout representing key infrastructure metrics (e.g., `\"20+ Yrs Craft\"`, `\"99.99% SLA\"`, `\"End-to-End Encryption\"`) with alive neon dots and ping animations.\n*   **20-Year Experience Timeline**: Interactive chronological list (2006 \342\200\224 2026) visualizing key metrics, supervisor leadership records, and custom collapsible system performance highlights.\n*   **Selected Creations Grid**: Immersive project showcase panel with visual category tab filters, custom card scale animations, and detailed focus drawers showing structural details, stack assembly, and mock codebase access coordinates.\n*   **Interactive Shell Console**: A fully integrated client command-line terminal with mock macOS action controls, reactive command execution (`help`, `about`, `skills`, `projects`, `contact`), and simple click-to-run quick shortcut pills.\n*   **Transactional Socket Form**: A responsive contact node with budget selection indicators, real-time feedback loaders, and secure SSL verified visual shields.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\216\254 Interaction Engine\n*   **Motion Transitions**: All layout changes, modal triggers, and section anchors are animated smoothly using **Framer Motion** configurations for realistic inertia bounces and fading entry flows.\n*   **Fluid Scrolling Anchors**: Integrates an elegant glassmorphic navbar capsule which dynamically tracks scroll coordinates to slide active indicator bubbles across anchors.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 211851904
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
