  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bold Typography\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bold Typography\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-100 font-sans w-full h-[768px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col relative\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center w-full mb-12\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"text-xs tracking-[0.3em] font-bold uppercase flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full\\\"></span>\\n      Alex Reed / Systems Architect\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-8 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\\\">Selected Works</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\\\">Philosophy</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors\\\">Stack</a>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-4 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full flex items-center px-1 cursor-pointer\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full ml-auto\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Grid -->\\n  <div class=\\\"flex-grow grid grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-end\\\">\\n    <!-- Column 1: Identity & Years -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-between h-full py-4\\\">\\n      <div>\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-blue-600 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-4\\\">Experience</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-5xl font-light leading-tight\\\">\\n          20<span class=\\\"text-neutral-600\\\">+</span>\\n          <br />\\n          Years of \\n          <br />\\n          <span class=\\\"italic font-serif\\\">Precision</span>\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\">\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-neutral-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Specialization</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm\\\">Distributed Cloud Architectures & <br/>High-Performance Frontend Systems</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-neutral-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Based in</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm\\\">San Francisco \342\200\224 London \342\200\224 Remote</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Column 2: The Big Name -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-5 h-full relative\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-[14rem] font-bold leading-[0.8] tracking-tighter text-neutral-900 select-none pointer-events-none\\\">\\n          ALEX<br/>REED\\n        </h1>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-end h-full pb-8\\\">\\n         <div class=\\\"bg-blue-600 p-6 rounded-tr-[4rem] w-64\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mb-2\\\">Currently Building</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium\\\">\\n              Scalable real-time visual collaboration tools for the next generation of engineers.\\n            </p>\\n         </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Column 3: Stats & Contact -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex flex-col justify-between h-full py-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"space-y-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"border-l border-neutral-800 pl-6\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-4 tracking-widest\\\">Recent Impact</h3>\\n          <ul class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n            <li class=\\\"group\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase\\\">Fintech Platform</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-sm group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors\\\">99.99% Uptime migration for 2M users</div>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"group\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase\\\">SaaS Startup</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-sm group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors\\\">Frontend performance optimization (40%\342\206\221)</div>\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"group\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase\\\">Global Media</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-sm group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors\\\">Custom Design System deployment</div>\\n            </li>\\n          </ul>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"border-l border-neutral-800 pl-6\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-4 tracking-widest\\\">Core Stack</h3>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">RUST</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">TYPESCRIPT</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">REACT</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">NEXT.JS</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">GQL</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 text-[10px] rounded\\\">AWS</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-black cursor-pointer transition-all\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-lg leading-none\\\">\342\206\227</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs tracking-widest font-bold\\\">\\n          LET\'S CONNECT\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- Bottom Accents -->\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-8 right-8 flex gap-2\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n  </div>\\n  \\n  <div class=\\\"absolute top-1/2 -right-8 -translate-y-1/2 rotate-90 opacity-20\\\">\\n    <p class=\\\"text-[8px] tracking-[2em] font-black uppercase\\\">\\n      CONSULTANCY \342\200\242 ARCHITECTURE \342\200\242 ENGINEERING \342\200\242 DESIGN\\n    </p>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
