kMode ? \"text-zinc-400\" : \"text-neutral-600\"}>{metric}</span>\n                        </li>\n                      ))}\n                    </ul>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Tags assembly */}\n                <div className=\"border-t border-dashed border-blue-500/15 pt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-zinc-500 font-bold uppercase mr-1\">\n                    ASSEMBLY STACK:\n                  </span>\n                  {activeProject.tags.map((t, idx) => (\n                    <span\n                      key={idx}\n                      className={`text-[10px] font-mono px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-md ${\n                        isDarkMode\n                          ? \"bg-neutral-900 border border-white/[0.04] text-zinc-300\"\n                          : \"bg-neutral-100 border border-black/[0.04] text-neutral-700\"\n                      }`}\n                    >\n                      {t}\n                    </span>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Sticky bottom CTA actions */}\n              <div className={`p-4 border-t flex items-center justify-end gap-3 ${\n                isDarkMode ? \"border-white/5 bg-zinc-950/60\" : \"border-black/5 bg-neutral-50/60\"\n              }`}>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setActiveProject(null)}\n                  className={`px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs font-semibold ${\n                    isDarkMode ? \"text-zinc-400 hover:text-white\" : \"text-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-900\"\n                  }`}\n                >\n                  Close\n                </button>\n                <a\n                  href=\"https://github.com/dhanush102003\"\n                  target=\"_blank\"\n                  rel=\"noreferrer\"\n                  className=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl bg-bl