    summary: "itboomi.com is the website for itboomi innovations, a software development company established in 2023[1][2][3][4][5]. Based in Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India, the company specializes in mobile app development, web development, digital marketing, and design[3][4][5][6][7].\n\nThere is no indication in the search results that \"itboomi.com\" offers a product specifically named \"sticky cards.\"\n\nHowever, \"Sticky Cards\" as a general term refers to a digital loyalty platform designed for businesses like restaurants, cafes, and quick-service establishments. This platform allows customers to join loyalty programs via QR codes and access digital cards through Apple & Google Wallet, offering features like automated rewards, push notifications, and geofence targeting[8][9]. There\'s also a \"Sticky Cards\" software specifically for cannabis dispensaries to manage loyalty programs[10].\n\nAdditionally, \"sticky notes\" can refer to digital applications for note-taking and organization, with various apps available for different devices and purposes[11][12]. There is also a feature within the Boomi platform (a different company) that allows users to create \"sticky notes for your process\" for internal referencing[13].\n\nSources:\n[1] [goodfirms.co](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG3m7-AhUVfQk_mdlVx-6paqhLdjLOU4rco-Yvta3-UNVeaz9uytS7h4VVQc8FY74rqaA9GtOxbTV-h2xZKh2XJB0Fb9jk2zZJDCmO9aB_CGC_RCymeXiH38IETTCYX6BtcTRhv4Mbq5_ywZJXGJpA=)\n[2] [techbehemoths.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE_Qq4riHt4xpKoBV_bRowRxyEp9Snj5p2pAUXDqn7QU7gVAvRMNSX_IKbCLagv27fy-0Kg42Gga4vNVdvVcksiZvWdlmvcPbv7Ms1XtvRHpRwsOpo2o-KybF6Pt8Zayl-F-qwjYzpkHMf93aHF_YSW)\n[3] [techreviewer.co](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHDR8Y5HS1MWcSYC5--Ub8w0YfU8JGm2I0RurHBs2WrH8V84WbtGZM6OvxDn8kFn08kMZrOjmprab7FChv293ABm5RPnLznDEO5DeEuEENlFcwVAqrl6mcsez87QiapnHwm5mz0ixczjXr0_P56zFwo)\n[4] [topdev