    thinking: "**Achieving a Clean Build**\n\nI\'ve achieved a completely clean compilation, free of warnings or errors. It\'s a testament to good coding. I\'ve successfully implemented the smooth, cinematic preloader as a fixed-overlay feature, which is a key component of the requested premium typographic landing animation.\n\n\n**Implementing Dynamic Progress Indicators**\n\nI\'m now focused on the preloader animation. I\'ve built a counter in `src/App.tsx` that goes from `00` to `100` with dynamic status updates like \"MOUNTING CORE KINETIC MATRICES...\" and styled it with a custom gradient and glow. Once done, the preloader smoothly slides up. I\'ve started the character-by-character masked split-text reveal animation and the parallax ribbons. I\'ve also refactored project cards into a CSS sticky stacking deck.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the core structural updates to your portfolio, introducing high-fidelity animations and scroll-bound stacking systems matching your selected themes:\n\n### 1. Cinematic Landing Typography Reveal\n*   **Monospace Preloader**: Created a full-screen, high-contrast boot sequence that counts from `00%` to `100%` with a glowing progress line and dynamic status updates (*\"Mounting Core Kinetic Matrices...\"*, *\"Compiling Bento Architectures...\"*).\n*   **Kinetic Split-Text Transition**: On completion, the loader slides out, triggering a staggered letter-split reveal. The display header *\"Meet Dhanush\"* uses customized cubic-beziers and spring physics to translate upward. Each letter is individually hover-interactive, scaling and glowing on pointer interaction.\n*   **Parallax Typographic Ribbons**: Added massive, semi-transparent background typographic banners that glide horizontally in opposite directions as you scroll, creating a three-dimensional parallax depth field.\n\n### 2. Sticky Stacking Cards (Our Core Disciplines)\nRefactored the project layout into a vertical sticky stacking card layout matching `itboomi.com`. The layout covers your four key specialties:\n1.  **Mobile App Development**: Focusing on native-speed iOS & Android engineering, 120Hz rendering architectures, and offline-first cache schemas.\n2.  **Web Development**: Featuring high-throughput distributed APIs, cluster microservices, and sub-35ms server-response metrics.\n3.  **UI/UX Design**: Illustrating token-driven design systems, kinetic micro-interactions, and accessible visual components (WCAG AA).\n4.  **Digital Marketing**: Highlighting optimized conversion funnels, micro-data schemas, and technical search engine performance clusters.\n\n*   **Stacking Mechanism**: Uses CSS `position: sticky` with incremental top offsets so cards stack beautifully on top of one another during scroll, with previous cards remaining visible as slivers at the top.\n*   **Visual Highlights**: Cards feature glowing category pills, high-quality descriptive panels, performance metrics, and immersive cover images that zoom dynamically on hover. All cards remain fully functional, opening interactive detail drawers upon inspection."
